content_request: Donne moi le volume d’appels par commune pour les clients Mass-Market

Requête SQL envoyée :

SELECT 
    r.year AS year,
    r.month AS month,
    r.ca_cr_commune AS commune,
    SUM(r.csu_mobile + r.div + r.expresso_mobile + r.fixe_expresso + 
        r.fixe_sonatel + r.orange + r.free + r.promobile + r.international) AS total_call_volume
FROM 
    reporting_monthly_voix AS r
WHERE 
    r.segment_marche LIKE '%Mass-Market%
GROUP BY 
    r.year, r.month, r.ca_cr_commune
ORDER BY 
    r.year DESC, r.month DESC, total_call_volume DESC;
